T1  - Reconsidering Openness in Organizational Communication
AU  - Eisenberg, Eric M.
AU  - Witten, Marsha G.
Y1  - 1987/07/01
PY  - 1987
DA  - 1987/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1987.4306557
