T1  - Convergence/Divergence: A Temporal Review of the Japanese Enterprise and Its Management
AU  - Dunphy, Dexter
Y1  - 1987/07/01
PY  - 1987
DA  - 1987/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1987.4306560
DO  - 10.5465/amr.1987.4306560
